#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&stage; is the presentations program in the &calligra; productivity suite. "
"Using &stage;, you can prepare a set of slides for use in an on-screen "
"slideshow or for printing. Your slides can include text and graphics in a "
"variety of formats, and of course, you can embed all sorts of objects using "
"KParts."
msgstr ""
"&kpresenter; ni i Amagaragaza Porogaramu in i &koffice; . &kpresenter; , A "
"Gushyiraho Bya Ibice ya:  Koresha in ku - Mugaragaza Cyangwa ya:  Icapa . "
"Ibice Gushyiramo Umwandiko na Ibishushanyo in A Bya Imiterere , na Bya , "
"Gutsindira Byose Bya Ibintu ikoresha . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
